race.comment: SWEET BUBBLES (8) is a consistent mare who comes here in peak condition and should run the trip. Took ground off Forbidden Riff when a tough third from back in the field over 2100m at Gosford. Gets the right run and the claim helps. LUNAR LOVER (2) proven at this trip and expected to return to form after disappointing when ninth over 1900m at Canterbury. Brings a solid set of figures and anywhere near his best would win this. MR FABULOUS (3) has been unlucky at his last couple of runs and has a win in him this prep. Gripped on late when a close-up fourth to STAY TUNED over this track and trip at latest. Tricky gate to navigate but not to be overlooked. STAY TUNED (1) chasing the hat-trick today after stretching out to this trip for the first time when a slick 2.25 len winner over this track and trip. Meets a few of these worse off at the weights but racing too well to dismiss.
